title: 2016 Week 17 review
itunes:title: 2016 Week 17 review
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, and Chris Wesseling – recap all the action from the final week of the NFL regular season which including the Redskins playoffs hopes being dashed in a close one against the Giants, and the Raiders falling to the 5th seed in the AFC. Plus, NFL Network’s Gregg Rosenthal joins the show to report live from what could be the final Chargers game in San Diego.
